  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_77543A80-1E4A-0135-0356-22000BC102FE" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In Course Navigation, click the <strong>Assignments </strong>link.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="add_assignment" data-step-uuid="6e767dcb-d4cc-43a4-a20a-a593349d1c8d">
