  <div id="text-content_77550E80-1E4A-0135-035E-22000BC102FE" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Click the <strong>Find</strong> button.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="configure_external_tool" data-step-uuid="928d7ee8-2fa8-43d3-b215-651b3fe27012">
    <h2 id="configure_external_tool" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Configure External Tool</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/001/716/130/original/b23a78b2-27db-4f15-a038-c79dadaaab31.png" srcset="" alt="Configure External Tool" height="405" width="400">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_77554340-1E4A-0135-0360-22000BC102FE" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Locate and select Office 365 Cloud Assignment [1].</p>
<p>If you want the assignment to load in a new tab, click the <strong>Load in a new tab</strong> checkbox [2]. Click the <strong>Select</strong> button [3].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
        <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-2" id="attach_file" data-step-uuid="484a40d3-4864-4ddb-a6f8-6a28f206a37d">
    <h3 id="attach_file" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Attach File</h3>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/003/384/106/original/837520bd-5f5e-44f8-907a-34bbf82c11f2.png" srcset="" alt="Attach File" height="434" width="828">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_775574C0-1E4A-0135-0362-22000BC102FE" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Locate and select the file you want to link to the assignment [1]. Click the <strong>Attach File</strong> button [2].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="select_tool" data-step-uuid="4d30d9d4-34a7-442a-9fab-21a932ab348c">
    <h2 id="select_tool" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Select Tool</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/000/781/185/original/ca47d3c6-b486-43a4-9a23-5a1dd62cef4e.png" srcset="" alt="Select Tool" height="405" width="403">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_7755A610-1E4A-0135-0364-22000BC102FE" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In the External Tool window, view the URL for your assignment file [1]. To select a different file, click the Office 365 link again. </p>
<p>If you want the assignment to load in a new tab, click the <strong>Load in a new tab</strong> checkbox [2]. </p>
<p>Click the <strong>Select </strong>button [3].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

